== Viewing

These slides are in pure HTML -- just view javaee-mvc-and-polymer.html and you're good to go!

== Building

The presentation slides are plain HTML and http://imakewebthings.com/deck.js/}[deck.js^], built using  http://asciidoctor.org[Asciidoctor^]. To generate all of the HTML slides, execute the included Grunt build script:

----
grunt build
----

To run a server or run examples, execute:

----
grunt server
----


